 White, L. H., (2005). The application of Geographic information and positioning systems to engineering related field activities within the Jamaica sugarcane industry. Proc Jamaican Association of Sugar Technologist Conference, Ocho Rios, Jamaica<br />
 <br />
 Wilson, M. R. (2005) Implementation of NIR Polarimetry in the Jamaica sugar industry. Conf. Third World Organization of Women Scientists (TWOWS), Bangalore India<br />
 <br />
 Wilson, M. R (2003). New Methods of Analysis for Raw Sugars, JAST 64 Proc. (in print)<br />
 <br />
 Wilson, M. R. (2001) 'Polarisation of cane juice using non-toxic clarifying reagents', West Indies Sugar Technologist (WIST) Proc. Trinidad and Tobago<br />
